<hr>
<strong>WORKS CITED</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a &#8216;Works Cited&#8217; entry at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of 
your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Author&#8217;s Name. &#34;Title of Article.&#34; <em>Title of Publication</em> day, month and 
	year of publication: page number(s). Medium of publication.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Author&#8217;s Name">Smith, Achiti</span>. 
	&#34;<span class="hover" title="Title of Article">Something Went Wrong in Plane Crash, Experts Say</span>.&#34;  
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of Publication">Herald Tribune</span></em> 
	<span class="hover" title="day, month and year of publication">15 Dec. 2056</span>: 
	<span class="hover" title="page number">A5</span>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Medium of publication">Print</span>.
</blockquote>
<br>
